WEBVTT

00:12:57.901 --> 00:13:01.560
the global commons
will continue to deteriorate,

00:13:01.584 --> 00:13:05.567
and everybody will be much worse off.

00:13:06.388 --> 00:13:10.904
We need to save ourselves
from the tragedy of the commons.

00:13:12.451 --> 00:13:18.093
So, I invite all of you
to embrace the global commons.

00:13:18.801 --> 00:13:22.641
Please do remember
that global commons do exist

00:13:22.665 --> 00:13:25.050
and are waiting for your stewardship.

00:13:26.609 --> 00:13:29.807
We all share one planet in common.